      <title>纽约铜期货价格徘徊在每磅 4 美元上方，吸引买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/copper-lures-buyers-as-new-york-futures-hover-above-4-a-pound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球需求强劲的担忧加剧，铜期货价格出现一系列下跌，但随后出现了购买兴趣的初步迹象，推动伦敦和纽约铜期货价格小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/copper-lures-buyers-as-new-york-futures-hover-above-4-a-pound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 16:37:10 GMT</pubDate>
